# Generated files where the generator IS the source of truth.
#
# `src/lib/types.ts` is emitted by `openapi-typescript` (via
# `pnpm types:gen` / `node scripts/gen-types.mjs`) from the committed
# `ui/openapi.json` snapshot. The `generated-artifacts-fresh` CI job
# (`infra_generated_artifact_freshness_gate`) regenerates the file
# and fails on `git status --porcelain` drift, so running prettier
# on it would produce bytes that differ from the canonical generator
# output and the gate would flap. Leave it in openapi-typescript's
# native format.
#
# `public/docs/*.md` is copied verbatim from `docs/08_guides/*.md`
# by `scripts/copy-docs.mjs`. Letting prettier reformat the public
# copy would cause the same drift between the source and the
# committed output.
src/lib/types.ts
public/docs/*.md
